# After snippet generation all snippet parameters will be stripped from
# the '$' characters and will be able to 'jump' between parameters with the 
# 'Tab' button.
# Syntax:
#  #         - comment line indicator
#  <name>=>  - snippet name line; start of the snippet section; name must be a ingle token without any delimiters 
#  $<value>$ - snippet parameter 
#  $|$       - special snippet parameter indicating the 
#              caret position after the snippet insertion is completed. 
